metadata.name: Yang Hao also collected
metadata.description:
the scroll of animal skin. The force field of chaos stone can not isolate the space force emanating from his inner world. Any object will be ingested as long as it is touched by the space fluctuation of the inner world without resistance.



"Ye FAN CRUSHED YOU WITH THE FIRE furnace, now I will bring you into the inner world, but only the same thing!" Yang Hao chuckled, then the figure flashed, disappeared in situ.
